\newlabel{fig:kafka_infra}{{5.2}{17}{CA-DQStream Kafka producer and consumer configuration. The Kafka Connect source ingests NYC TLC Parquet files into the \texttt {taxi-nyc-raw} topic, while Flink consumers subscribe to all seven topics for pipeline processing}{figure.caption.18}{}}
